            {
              "enText": "<b>Lesson 14 • Taking Credit for Good Results</b>"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "When United Supply Company launches their website three weeks ahead of schedule, there's more than one person ready to take credit."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Kurt:</b> Wow, Bob, that's a first for this company! How did you <b>pull that off</b>?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Bob:</b> I <b>burned the midnight oil</b> over these past few weeks. I <b>worked my tail off</b>. Sometimes things would get tough, but I always <b>kept my eye on the prize</b>."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Tara:</b> Let's not forget about Jim in technical support. He really <b>hunkered down</b> these past few days, working <b>around the clock</b>."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Bob:</b> Yeah, Jim's a real <b>team player</b>. He helped a lot."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Kurt:</b> Well, that's not surprising. Jim's always ready to <b>pitch in</b>."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Bob:</b> Of course, you deserve a <b>pat on the back</b>, too, Kurt. None of this would've been possible without your leadership."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Kurt:</b> <b>All in a day's work</b>. Providing great leadership <b>comes with the territory</b>. Well, time for some <b>R&R</b>. I'm off to Florida to play golf for a few days. See you next week!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
